    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a great start for the students. Some of my more skeptical students might argue that this idea is just a way for judges to make up new laws instead of actually following what's written in the Constitution. How should I address those criticisms in the lesson?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
